. Otra lâ”œآ،nea de â”œأ­rboles, un poco mâ”œأ­s al fondo, seâ”œâ–’ala el cauce del Huerva.", "year": 1923, "year_from": 1923, "year_to": 1923, "era": "Anos 20", "zone": "UNIVERSIDAD", "lat": 41.63133, "lng": -0.89516, "image_url": "https://ktnavneugmimhdvpnnga.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/uploads/15270757968.webp", "thumb_url": "https://ktnavneugmimhdvpnnga.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/uploads/thumbs/15270757968.webp", "source": "https://www.flickr.com/photos/zaragozaantigua/15270757968/", "author": "Zaragoza Antigua (Flickr)", "rights": "Uso educativo", "tags": []}, {"id": 21578, "title": "Puente de Santa Isabel c.1923", "description": "Paso de carro con cuadrâ”œâ•‘pedos, proveniente del barrio de Santa Isabel, transitando por el puente de Santa Isabel sobre el râ”œآ،o Gâ”œأ­llego en direcciâ”œâ”‚n a Zaragoza. Fuente: Foto Jesâ”œâ•‘s Cormâ”œأ­n. AMZ.", "year": 1923, "year_from": 1923, "year_to": 1923, "era": "Anos 20", "zone": "EL RABAL", "lat": 41.671082, "lng": -0.842258, "image_url": "https://ktnavneugmimhdvpnnga.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/uploads/24276819414.webp", "thumb_url": "https://ktnavneugmimhdvpnnga.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/uploads/thumbs/24276819414.webp", "source": "https://www.flickr.com/photos/zaragozaantigua/24276819414/", "author": "Zaragoza Antigua (Flickr)", "rights": "Uso educativo", "tags": []}, {"id": 23742, "title": "Puente sobre el Gâ”œأ­llego 1895", "description": "Puente colgado sobre el râ”œآ،o Gâ”œأ­llego.", "year": 1895, "year_from": 1895, "year_to": 1895, "era": "Siglo XIX", "zone": "EL RABAL", "lat": 41.670914, "lng": -0.842028, "image_url": "https://ktnavneugmimhdvpnnga.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/uploads/14777528109.webp", "thumb_url": "https://ktnavneugmimhdvpnnga.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/uploads/thumbs/14777528109.webp", "source": "https://www.flickr.com/photos/zaragozaantigua/14777528109/", "author": "Zaragoza Antigua (Flickr)", "rights": "Uso educativo", "tags": []}, {